## Problem [/problems/{problem_id}]
+ Parameters
    + problem_id: (required, string) - Problem ID given in the response header when sending a math problem

### Retrieve result of a specific problem [GET]
+ Response 200 (application/json)
    {
        "problem_id": "bdmb8cboo3smi6jgiai0",
        "operation": "addition",
        "input_1": 1,
        "input_2": 1,
        "answer": 2
    }